---
import MainLayouts from '../layouts/Main-Layouts.astro';
---

<MainLayouts subtitle="Our Story" title="Taranium">
  <div class="relative w-full pt-[10rem] pb-20 px-4 md:px-6 lg:px-10 min-h-[calc(100vh-5rem)]">
    <div class="max-w-[70rem] mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-center text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-[45px] text-white font-clashDisplay font-semibold tracking-[2px] sm:tracking-[3px] uppercase mb-10">OUR STORY</h1>

      <div class="relative">
        <div class="absolute left-4 md:left-1/2 transform md:-translate-x-1/2 h-full w-0.5 border border-dashed border-[#666666] timeline-dashed"></div>
        <div class="space-y-24">
          <!-- Item 1 (tidak berubah) -->
          <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center justify-between">
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 md:pr-8 text-left md:text-right order-2 md:order-none pl-12 md:pl-0 mb-3 md:mb-0">
              <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-white">2011</h3>
              <h4 class="text-2xl text-white mt-1 uppercase">The Seed of Innovation</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute left-0 md:left-1/2 transform md:-translate-x-1/2 w-8 h-8 bg-[#101010] border-4 border-[#D0B2FF] rounded-full z-10"></div>
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 pl-12 md:pl-8 order-3 md:order-none">
              <div class="bg-[#2C2C2C] border border-[#c2c2c2] p-5 rounded-lg">
                <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-white leading-6 md:leading-7">
                  In 2011, the world of blockchain was still in its infancy, but we were already dreaming big. Our journey began with a single mining server, nestled in a small, dimly lit room. It was more than just a piece of hardware; it
                  was a symbol of our belief in the transformative power of blockchain technology. Those early days were marked by curiosity, late nights, and a relentless pursuit of knowledge. We weren't just mining cryptocurrency; we were
                  mining the future.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Item 2 (diubah) -->
          <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center justify-between">
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 md:pr-8 order-2 md:order-none pl-12 md:pl-0">
              <div class="md:hidden mb-3">
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-white">2017</h3>
                <h4 class="text-2xl text-white mt-1 uppercase">Building the Dream Team</h4>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-[#2C2C2C] border border-[#c2c2c2] p-5 rounded-lg md:text-right">
                <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-white leading-6 md:leading-7">
                  As the years passed, our vision grew clearer, but we knew that to make a real impact, we needed a team as passionate and determined as we were. In 2017, the foundation for Taranium was laid with the formation of our core
                  team. Each member brought a unique skill set and shared a common goal: to create something revolutionary. Together, we spent countless hours brainstorming, researching, and refining our ideas. This was the year when our
                  dream started to take shape.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute left-0 md:left-1/2 transform md:-translate-x-1/2 w-8 h-8 bg-[#101010] border-4 border-[#D0B2FF] rounded-full z-10"></div>
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 pl-12 md:pl-8 text-left order-3 md:order-none hidden md:block">
              <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-white">2017</h3>
              <h4 class="text-2xl text-white mt-1 uppercase">Building the Dream Team</h4>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Item 3 (tidak berubah) -->
          <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center justify-between">
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 md:pr-8 text-left md:text-right order-2 md:order-none pl-12 md:pl-0 mb-3 md:mb-0">
              <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-white">2021</h3>
              <h4 class="text-2xl text-white mt-1 uppercase">The Birth of Taranium Foundation</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute left-0 md:left-1/2 transform md:-translate-x-1/2 w-8 h-8 bg-[#101010] border-4 border-[#D0B2FF] rounded-full z-10"></div>
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 pl-12 md:pl-8 order-3 md:order-none">
              <div class="bg-[#2C2C2C] border border-[#c2c2c2] p-5 rounded-lg">
                <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-white leading-6 md:leading-7">
                  By 2021, the blockchain landscape had evolved dramatically, and so had our ambitions. It was time to bring our ideas to the world. The Taranium Foundation was initiated as a beacon of innovation, aimed at empowering the
                  next generation of Web3 projects. With a solid foundation and a clear mission, we set out to create a blockchain network that would serve as the backbone for decentralized applications, DeFi, and beyond. This was the
                  beginning of a new chapter in our journey—a chapter defined by purpose and potential.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Item 4 (diubah) -->
          <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center justify-between">
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 md:pr-8 order-2 md:order-none pl-12 md:pl-0">
              <div class="md:hidden mb-3">
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-white">2023</h3>
                <h4 class="text-2xl text-white mt-1 uppercase">A NETWORK LIKE NO OTHER</h4>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-[#2C2C2C] border border-[#c2c2c2] p-5 rounded-lg md:text-right">
                <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-white leading-6 md:leading-7">
                  After years of hard work, trials, and triumphs, 2023 marked the official development of the Taranium blockchain network. This was more than just a technological achievement; it was a realization of our collective vision.
                  Our network was designed with scalability, security, and sustainability at its core, ready to support a wide range of applications from the metaverse to real-world asset tokenization. The Taranium blockchain wasn't just
                  another network; it was a platform built to empower and elevate the Web3 ecosystem.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute left-0 md:left-1/2 transform md:-translate-x-1/2 w-8 h-8 bg-[#101010] border-4 border-[#D0B2FF] rounded-full z-10"></div>
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 pl-12 md:pl-8 text-left order-3 md:order-none hidden md:block">
              <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-white">2023</h3>
              <h4 class="text-2xl text-white mt-1 uppercase">A NETWORK LIKE NO OTHER</h4>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Item 5 (tidak berubah) -->
          <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center justify-between">
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 md:pr-8 text-left md:text-right order-2 md:order-none pl-12 md:pl-0 mb-3 md:mb-0">
              <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-white">2024</h3>
              <h4 class="text-2xl text-white mt-1 uppercase">Legal Formation and Future Horizons</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute left-0 md:left-1/2 transform md:-translate-x-1/2 w-8 h-8 bg-[#101010] border-4 border-[#D0B2FF] rounded-full z-10"></div>
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 pl-12 md:pl-8 order-3 md:order-none">
              <div class="bg-[#2C2C2C] border border-[#c2c2c2] p-5 rounded-lg">
                <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-white leading-6 md:leading-7">
                  In 2024, Taranium took its final step towards becoming a global leader in blockchain technology. We officially formed the Taranium Foundation as a legal entity, solidifying our commitment to transparency, integrity, and
                  innovation. With our legal foundation in place, we are now poised to lead Indonesia—and the world—into a new era of decentralized possibilities. But our journey doesn't end here; it's only the beginning. As we look to the
                  future, we are more determined than ever to push the boundaries of what blockchain can achieve.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayouts>

<style>
  .timeline-dashed {
    --dash-length: 10px;
    --gap-length: 10px;
    background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, #666666 var(--dash-length), transparent var(--dash-length));
    background-size: 2px calc(var(--dash-length) + var(--gap-length));
    border: none;
  }
</style>
